  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      NovellusDx is developing a diagnostic platform for the personalized cancer therapy based on
      patient derived tumor tissue. The assay is able to sense activating mutations by monitoring
      their effect on a chip-based device.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
